   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Livelihood Improvment Project Takhar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">The main objective of phase II is to create new farm and off-farm revenues (income generation pillar) and extend basic health services to women and children (health pillar). LIPT is well embedded in the Afghan National Development Strategy (ANDS), which acts as a poverty reduction strategy (PRS) for the Government of Afghanistan and its partners and implicitly recognises the need for direct support to local development activities.</narrative>
